The CanoScan LiDE120 Color Image Scanner is a compact scanner that offers advanced features and affordability. Plus, it scans fast, creating a letter size color scan in approximately 16 seconds.4 What’s more, the LiDE120 scanner uses one USB cable for both data and power, so plugging in is easy. Dynamic security enabled printer. Intended to be used with cartridges using only HP electronic circuitry. Cartridges with modified or non-HP electronic circuitry may not work, and those that work today may not work in the future.
Save time and money with HP's most affordable wireless all-in-one printer to date. With a hassle-free setup and easy printing from your mobile devices, the HP DeskJet 2600 All-in-One removes the complications of your everyday printing needs.
Get the HP All-in-One Printer like the HP DeskJet 2630 which helps you save on time and money. Its very easy to setup and allows you to print from your mobile devices.

Features

Print from your mobile devices without hassle.

With a simple setup from your smartphone, you can manage your printing from a variety of smartphones and tablets even when you're on the go. You can also scan while you're on the move with the HP All-In-One Printer Remote app.


Save Money on Ink

With HP high-yield ink cartridges, you'll get twice as many pages of high-quality prints, thanks to the all-in-one built to be reliable.


Wireless Printing, Copying and Scanning

The HP 2630 Wireless Printer has wireless printing, scanning and copying capabilities. The compact design means that the printer can be used even in small spaces. The output tray, which minimizes space when closed reduces jams and holds up to 25 sheets when in use.

Name: Long Range USB WiFi Adapter - AWUSO36H
Keywrds: Long Range USB WiFi Adapter - AWUSO36H
Description:
The Alfa AWUS036H is a 1000mW high-power long range wireless 802.11g Wi-Fi USB adapter.  What sets this USB device apart from other USB adapters on the market is that it has an RP-SMA antenna connector so that you can add an external antenna to boost your wireless range. This is the newest version from Alfa with a 5 dBi gain rubber duck antenna in retail box.

It comes with a stunning 1000mW output power. So if you are looking for a device to connect to an outdoor 2.4 GHz antenna, such as on a boat or an RV, this is a perfect solution. Because it is a USB adapter, it works on any computer (desktop or laptop) that has a USB port and it outperforms wireless cards that are built in to newer laptops. 

Adding this to your laptop or desktop computer will enhance range and signal quality at longer distances. And works with Win98SE/200/ME/XP, Windows Vista, Windows 7, Linux (kernel 2.6.6 and later) and Macintosh (OS version 10.4). And the necessary drivers for ALL of these operating systems are included on CD-ROM.
ShortDescription:
Key Features
  • 4-inch 5 DdBi & 9 DdBi Screw-On Swivel Rubber Antenna
  • High security 64/128/256bit WEP Encryption
  • Compact size for flexibility
  • Colour: White
